      "writtenOn": "2026-06-09T10:02:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, there will be additional commits on top of this one. Immediately after this commit, we need to implement the interfaces (ComponentIntegrity and TrustedInterface). For that, we need the D-Bus objects in place, and those objects will require names.\n\nCurrently, the object names will be based on the EIDs of the MCTP-discovered objects. Later, we plan to replace those EID-based names with the corresponding inventory object names. So this commit is required now because the next commit depends on it. I can have the follow-up commit ready as well.\n\nI\u0027m not sure why we\u0027re blocked on the naming of the D-Bus object path, especially since the current naming is intended as an intermediate step and will be updated once the inventory object names become available.",
